version_description: Apparently, most tab authors have problems correctly translating the Drop C tabs into chords, so here's my take on this song - including power chords and strumming patterns.
Song is in Key of C, no Capo.
Specific, corrected chords true to the key, labeled and timed sections, riffs, strumming pattern.
Original chords by Romantic485. Added F# in the repeating riff in the verse.
The version was taken of an acoustic cover in addition it contains the original letter of the version of the film "The Shack". https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oW9jV-xV6kg.
